#  Day 43 – AI Workflow Architect

##  Project Overview

AI Workflow Architect is an interactive web application that helps users design complete end-to-end workflows for different domains using AI-powered recommendations. The application breaks complex processes into structured stages, recommends suitable AI tools, provides prompt examples, and highlights future automation opportunities.

---

##  Objective

To create an interactive workflow planner that helps users understand how tasks move from planning to execution while leveraging AI tools to improve productivity and decision-making.

---

##  Features

- Interactive Workflow Builder
- End-to-End Workflow Stages
- Objectives & Task Breakdown
- AI Tool Recommendations
- Alternative AI Tools
- Prompt Examples
- Best Practices
- Common Mistakes
- Expected Outputs
- Time Estimates
- Workflow Diagram
- Decision Tree
- Progress Tracking
- Notes & Bookmarks
- Workflow Summary
- Recommended AI Stack
- Learning Resources
- Future Automation Opportunities
- Local Storage Support
- Printable Workflow Guide
- Responsive Dark UI

---

##  Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- Vanilla JavaScript
- Local Storage API

